ZE_RANDOMIZER (CS:S Version)

CS:GO Version

A collaborative project made by:
> Raphi: Fall Guys, Karting, Prison, The Sims, Simon Say, Scoobydoo, Endings (Laserfag, BeatSaber, and THE END)
> Hichatu: Spawn, Non Euclidian Geometry, Randomaze, Laserfag, Items
> King Buzzo: Strafe Escape, Flying Wheels, Deathrun
> Qazlll456: Magical Scale Area Test Field BOAT BOAT BOAT
> m4dara: Power Plant
> yesme: Nightmare
> 4Echo: Ratway
> Frenchy: Dark World
> LESARA: Pirate war
> chinny: Fortress Defense
> Ordiaxer: FEZ

This map contains 20 different levels. Each time you'll beat one level, you will be teleported to another one. After beating 5, 10, and 20 levels in a row, you'll be able to vote for an Ending. 
Obviously, the best endings are harder to reach.

You can easily play this map for fun, or decide to train and try hard to reach the 2nd and 3rd ending.

Thanks everybody for the support, and we hope to see you reaching last ending... one day!

=======================================================
This version already need a stripper to work well, feel free to send us feedbacks if you notice any issue
